    <description>This is a Schedule-Triggered Flow.
The flow starts by querying scheduled campaigns where the &apos;Lecture__c&apos; field is true. It then checks the proximity of each event to the current date and sets a reminder (&apos;Trigger_SFMC_Reminder__c&apos;) accordingly. The reminders can be set for 28 days, 10 days, 7 days, 1 day, or today before the event. Finally, it updates the campaign members with the new reminder values.

Several objects and their fields worth mentioning. Below are the details (the format is given as: object_name - field_name: interaction)
  * Campaign - Status : Filters campaigns based on status and Lecture__c field
  * CampaignMember - Remaining_Tickets__c : Updates campaign members with new reminder values</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>IsEventIn10Days</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>IF( DATEVALUE({!$Record.Start__c}) = TODAY() + 10, TRUE, FALSE )</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>IsEventIn1Day</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>IF( DATEVALUE({!$Record.Start__c}) = TODAY() + 1, TRUE, FALSE )</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>IsEventIn28Days</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>IF( DATEVALUE({!$Record.Start__c}) = TODAY() + 28, TRUE, FALSE )</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>IsEventIn7Days</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>IF( DATEVALUE({!$Record.Start__c}) = TODAY() + 7, TRUE, FALSE )</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>IsEventToday</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>IF( DATEVALUE({!$Record.Start__c}) = TODAY(), TRUE, FALSE )</expression>
    </formulas>
